124 And he to me: “You know that the place is round;
125 and although you have come a long way,
126 yet on the left, going down to the bottom,

127 you have not yet turned all the way around the circle;
128 therefore, if something new appears to us,
129 it should not bring wonder to your face.”

124 Kaj li al mi: “Vi scias ke la loko estas ronda;
125 kaj kvankam vi venis tre longen,
126 tamen maldekstre, malsuprenirante al fundo,

